{"tid":856730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(尋藥)綠色扁鐵盒","createTime":"2018-10-10T17:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T02:43:29.000Z","uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9eec72cf8d73ff36592c4260144e78f30daa0b8f","tid":856730,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:32:21.000Z","msg":"想搵返一隻藥膏<br />\n係專搽粉刺或皮膚問題<br />\n<br />\n係一個綠色好扁鐵盒<br />\n類似凡士林潤唇膏個盒但再扁一半<br />\n<br />\n裡面係白色藥膏<br />\n搽落皮膚都會白色，隔一段時間會乾硬左<br />\n唔係喜療妥果種軟膏同搽完會吸收無色<br />\n<br />\n藥性係偏刺激<br />\n搽皮膚患處會那，甚至有灼熱感<br />\n唔係滋潤溫和類<br />\n<br />\n十幾年前已經有<br />\n但近幾年唔見，唔知係咪停左產<br />\n但每次有皮膚問題都好見效<br />\n<br />\n全能連登幫唔幫到手"},{"pid":"b7e998ee1e7b788dcbfa092885781b5bd0475494","tid":856730,"uid":12131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"Nixoderm?"},{"pid":"380dd8962236afff235bd0b02c06ae42a6a895bf","tid":856730,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e998ee1e7b788dcbfa092885781b5bd0475494","tid":856730,"uid":12131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"Nixoderm?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T18:03:10.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n90%係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為好細個用，早幾年用晒買唔到，上網睇圖好大機會係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便問一問，係咪一般藥房都有得買，同埋乜人都搽得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9718bafe518d7d16b1db68de1779b34d3017d3a2","tid":856730,"uid":12131,"like":